---
// No client-side interactivity needed for this component
---

<section class="w-full bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    {/* Header */}
    <div class="mb-8 relative">
      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-4 px-8 rounded-lg relative">
        {/* Primary accent left */}
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-4 h-full bg-[#25D007] rounded-l-lg"></div>
        {/* Primary accent right */}
        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-4 h-full bg-[#25D007] rounded-r-lg"></div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center relative z-10">
          Privacy Policy
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Main Content */}
    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        At I8 Fun, your privacy is our top priority. We are fully committed to safeguarding your personal information and earning your trust. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, protect, and manage your data when you access our services.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Information We Collect</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We collect the following types of information to provide you with the best gaming experience:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Personal Details:</strong> This includes your name, mobile number, email address, and password, collected during registration.</li>
        <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> We gather details about your device type, operating system, and IP address to enhance performance and ensure security.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We track your game activity, rewards history, referrals, and transaction logs to optimize your gaming and earnings experience.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Why We Collect Your Information</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The information we collect serves several important purposes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>To create and manage your account, ensuring a seamless experience.</li>
        <li>To deliver a smooth and enjoyable gaming environment.</li>
        <li>To administer rewards and referral programs effectively.</li>
        <li>To protect platform security and prevent fraudulent activities.</li>
        <li>To provide updates, bonuses, and customer support communications.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Data Protection & Security</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We employ advanced encryption and security protocols to protect your personal information. Rest assured, your data is securely stored and will never be shared, sold, or rented to any third parties without your explicit consent. We implement industry-standard security measures to safeguard your information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Third-Party Links</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our platform may contain links to external websites. However, we are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies separately before providing any personal information to third-party websites.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Your Rights</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        You have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Access your personal information at any time</li>
        <li>Request corrections to your data</li>
        <li>Delete your account and associated data</li>
        <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
        <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Data Retention</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. When your data is no longer needed, we will securely delete or anonymize it in accordance with applicable laws and regulations.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Updates to This Policy</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any significant changes through the app or via email. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your information.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h3>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or how we handle your personal information, please contact our customer support team. We are committed to addressing your inquiries promptly and ensuring your privacy is protected at all times.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-semibold">
        Last Updated: January 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
